"topics" LEFT OUTER JOIN "categories" ON "categories"."id" = "topics"."category_id" WHERE (topics.archetype <> 'private_message') AND (COALESCE(categories.topic_id, 0) <> topics.id) AND "topics"."visible" = TRUE AND (topics.deleted_at IS NULL) AND (topics.category_id IS NULL or topics.category_id IN (1)) AND (pinned_globally AND  pinned_at IS NOT NULL ) ORDER BY topics.bumped_at DESC LIMIT 30
